bool isRotation(string s1, string s2) {
    if (s1.length() != s2.length())
        return false;

    string temp = s1 + s1;
    return temp.find(s2) != string::npos;
}

Time & Space

Time: O(n)

Space: O(n)

I check if the second string is a substring of the first string concatenated with itself.‚Äù
